A five-year-old boy has been killed in central India after being dragged from his home by a leopard.

The leopard attacked the boy on Monday evening as he was visiting the outdoor bathroom in the courtyard of his home in a village in Chhattisgarh state.

This is thought to have been the second deadly attack by the same leopard, local police said today.

